OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with a few showers, mainly in
OL,7,Fthe north and west. These becoming
OL,8,Fmore frequent after midnight, and
OL,9,Fmerging to give more persistent rain,
OL,10,Falthough some southern and eastern
OL,11,Fparts remaining dry throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FOutbreaks of rain becoming
OL,14,Fwidespread through the morning. These
OL,15,Feasing from the northwest, but could
OL,16,Fpersist into the evening across some
OL,17,Fsouthern areas. Turning breezy,
OL,18,Fespecially along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
