OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCold
OL,6,Fstart Sunday, perhaps frosty, then dry
OL,7,Fwith sunny spells. Band of rain clears
OL,8,Fsouth early Monday, followed by
OL,9,Fbrighter spells. Further rain
OL,10,Fovernight and Tuesday morning, with
OL,11,Fshowers following.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
